@startuml
title Sequence: Create Customer

actor Client
Client -> CustomerController: POST /api/customers\n{customer JSON}
CustomerController -> CustomerService: create(customer)
CustomerService -> CustomerRepository: findByDocumentTypeAndDocumentNumber()
CustomerRepository --> CustomerService: Mono.empty()
CustomerService -> CustomerRepository: save(customer)
CustomerRepository --> CustomerService: savedCustomer
CustomerService --> CustomerController: savedCustomer
CustomerController --> Client: 201 Created + customer JSON
@enduml